\begin{frame}{Use of support and resistance}
As a result, support at resistance are used for 
\pause
\begin{itemize}[<+-| alert@+>]
\item Identifying when sentiment has changed
\item Setting \textbf{Take-profit}
\item Setting \textbf{Stop-loss} 
\end{itemize}
\pause
However, 
\pause
\begin{block}{}
